body: Hi Majed, In this error, because there is no zone named "CoolZone". CoolZone in additionalstrings will have to reference the name of a Zone that you have assigned(test_room). They must have the same name. [](http://api.ning.com/files/F*OBLvkzUL-Pz33KYAbkJKrmEjNNqF0*N7OjAWKTheNagJ1GPpBju0waEPZp9QseBZ7ocne6GMAffCq6sZPVk2BrvWI00Tp-/Image1.png) Also, see [this](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/group/ladybug/forum/topics/water-and-vegetation-features-in-honeybee?commentId=2985220%3AComment%3A1575803&groupId=2985220%3AGroup%3A658987) discussion for more info. -Omid
